<figureCitation box="[703,786,1002,1028]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–16" captionStartId="4.[151,269,1951,1975]" captionTargetBox="[163,1407,230,1931]" captionTargetId="figure-52@4.[151,1436,194,1931]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 10–16. Species of Pythamus. heads (10–12) and forewings (13–16). 10, 13. Pythamus biramosus sp. nov.; 11, 14. P. bispinosus sp. nov.; 12, 15. P. montanus sp. nov.; 16. P. dealbatus Melichar." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5087900" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5087900/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">Fig. 16</figureCitation>
hyaline.
</paragraph>
